{"id":149592,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/简讯：阿根廷乘客放火烧列车撒气/","date":"2011-05-03T16:30:29Z","modified":"2011-05-03T16:30:29Z","title":"简讯：阿根廷乘客放火烧列车撒气","content":"<div>\n<p>在阿根廷，由于火车严重晚点，愤怒的乘客向三趟列车纵火。</p>\n<p>情绪激动的乘客还把其中一趟列车的司机和检票员，以及铁路工作人员推下列车。</p>\n<p>这三起涉及数十名乘客的纵火事件几乎同时发生在该国首都布宜诺斯艾利斯附近的3座火车站。</p>\n<p>当地警方说，一些乘客还洗劫了其中一个火车站的售票处。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2011/05/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/wiPZ96iV2oy2NkUx9D-wrQZjTZ0/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/wiPZ96iV2oy2NkUx9D-wrQZjTZ0/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/wiPZ96iV2oy2NkUx9D-wrQZjTZ0/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/wiPZ96iV2oy2NkUx9D-wrQZjTZ0/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/hQWNL7o3bJg\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}